The paper discusses a new system for secure cover file of hidden data using statistical steganography techniques. This involves hiding information within the image page of an executable file, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). Additionally, the use of image processing techniques to embed the data within the image page suggests a connection to multimedia (cs.MM) and computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed system also involves statistical analysis to ensure the hidden data is not easily detectable, which could fall under machine learning (cs.LG) or software engineering (cs.SE).
